                          Caganers Celebrities - Caganer.com follow us on: Language:              WelcomeMy account ...My wishlistMy cartLogin  Shopping Cart 0 Item - Items -  $0.00          Cart     0 Products Product   (empty)No products 0,00 € Total Checkout         Menu News Collection Typical Catalan Traditions Other territories Comic Sports Professions Animals Resin Caganers Digital world Celebrities Universal Musicians Cinema Politicians Athletes FC Barcelona CombosHome  News   Collection Typical CatalanTraditionsOther territoriesComicSportsProfessionsAnimalsResin CaganersDigital world  Celebrities UniversalMusiciansCinemaPoliticiansAthletesFC Barcelona  Combos  Home / CelebritiesIn this section we intend to offer a range of Caganers that can be placed easily in the world of celebrities. That is the reason why we have added several sections, among which you can find actors, singers, football players and other sportmen, politicians, members of the Royal Family and immortal figures. Since they have done a good job, we pay tribute to their career with a Caganer in order to bring them luck. In 2002 we elaborated the first Caganers —Jordi Pujol, Pasqual Maragall and Artur Mas, three Catalan politicians— and it was such a success that we put heart into continue the series. Currently there are a lot of celebrities that feel proud of their Caganer, check them out!Subcategories   UniversalThis sub-category has remained a hodgepodge with Caganers that would need a whole section itselves for its peculiarity. This miscellany lead to a very special corner with emblematic characters such the famous dragon from Park Güell, the Dalai Lama, Che Guevara, Shakespeare, the Quijote or the Statue of Liberty. Most of them are clients' requests: they know it will bring calm and luck to their home!   MusiciansNowadays there is a huge number of singers onto the stage, so we could not miss a section dedicated to those characters who get along with us in a very special way: through music. Our collection of Caganers that sing goes over the musical history from pioners like John Lennon and Elvis Presley to contemporary artists like Shakira.   CinemaIn our Celebrity Section, we could not resist turning up some actors and actresses that marked a milestone into Caganers. Some of them have been such an icon that have become universal sex symbols or have been the promoters of a new style or school. Two good examples would be the unmistakable Groucho Marx or the delicious Marilyn Monroe. Who has not dreamt about having their charming?   PoliticiansPoliticians are in charge of organizing our cities and States, of bringing order and of managing culture, economy, relations between nations, education and justice —among other issues. Greeks were the inventors of democracy, but since men live in community it has prevailed a governance body that directs the society. Currently, policy has evolved in many directions giving cause for several ideologies and doctrines, some of which ended up as a conflict of interest. Without any intention of offending, we offer replicas in a Caganer format of this group of people called politicians, who manage to be heard and face this world we live. In this section you will find personalities like Donald Trump, José María Aznar, Artur Mas, François Hollande, Fidel Castro o Silvio Berlusconi.   AthletesWe are not here to deny that football is a major sport, although in this section you will find some of the most outstanding sporties at a national and international level —and even some prominent figures of the last Olympic Games. Now, if you are a sports lover, you won’t be disappointed with any of the Caganers nor their corresponding accesories: Rafa Nadal with his racket, Fernando Alonso with his helmet, Tiger Woods with his golf club and Cristiano Ronaldo with his T-shirt.   FC BarcelonaWith a team as famous as FC Barcelona, we are honoured to dedicate a whole section to this organisation and to some players that have been —or are— essentials for the history of the Club. It seemed interesting to join together to important aspects of the Catalan tradition —Caganers and Barça— in a single little figurine. As a result of this blending of cultures, in our blue and red corner you will find famous players like Messi, Neymar, Puyol and Piqué. Note that all the products we sell are official and licensed so that most of the Barcelona Football Club players have a ceramic Caganer that honours them.  Wishlist No productsSend a message   Subject Heading Customer serviceWebmaster  Email address  Message    My accountMy accountMy ordersMy credit slipsMy addressesMy personal infoLoginMy vouchersSign outLegalShipping and PaymentCondiciones de usoGeneral conditions of contractPolítica de privacidad y cookiesFAQLegal noticeInformationWho we areThe Caganer's historyThe workshopVisits to workshopWhere to buyFairesCaganer as a giftProfessionalsSocial responsibilityWe ship worldwideContact usSite MapWhere to buySearchContact usCopyright © 2016 Caganer.com - Av.Francesc Macià nº11 - Torroella de Montgrí - Catalonia - (0034) 972980394 - info@caganer.com
