José María Aznarprime minister of Spain



Written By:
The Editors of Encyclopædia Britannica


See Article History






Alternative Title:
		José María Aznar López



Jose Maria Aznar
Prime minister of Spain





Also known asJosé María Aznar LópezbornFebruary 25, 1953 (age 64)Madrid, Spaintitle / officeprime minister, Spain (1996-2004)political affiliationPopular Party


View Biographies Related To
